title: Help  Riot if u are here !!
body: I had AFK for 20min and i finished all the 5 games for the AFK. at the last game of the AFK after it i get again AFK for 20min idk why so i need help with that Riot as fast as possible. Thx

replies.body: I went ahead and pulled up your match history and it looks like something must have caused you to leave the last game in your LPQ. If you ever AFK or unintentionally leave a match while in low-priority queue, you will most likely get another round of delayed matches.
